      "created_at": "2021-10-12T12:59:19.825Z",
      "cooked": "<p>“Gjuri i Ahedës”, ose ajo qe Godard kish parashikuar ketu e 30 vite më parë :</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/f/d/fd524a356e45a1b5b665cc96141f417eb3c7b811.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"A8Z6wFEZpi1WDvWVxuMH6ExyknL\" width=\"507\" height=\"188\"></p>",
